4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bongani, swisher, prince
4 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, pony, rabbit
 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 3. the police-officer is not to the left of the bongani-smoker##8
 4. the designer is between the firefighter and the manager##2
 5. the designer is not the owner of the pony##6
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
 8. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
 9. the designer is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5
10. the person who's hobby is camping is in an odd position##4
11. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
12. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
13. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
14. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's sport is cycling##1
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the left of the prince-smoker##8
16. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
17. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who's sport is rowing##1
18. the person who's sport is rowing is not the firefighter##6
19. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
20. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the designer##5
21. the firefighter is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5

.:: Answer ::.
